        <a href="/about" class="text-decoration-none text-muted">About</a>
      </nav>
      <a href="/estimate" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Solar Panel Installation Guide & Payback Estimator (India)</h2>

    <div class="card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5>Requirements for Solar Panel Installation in India:</h5>
        <ul>
          <li>Open rooftop or land space with sufficient sunlight (ideally south-facing)</li>
          <li>Approval from local DISCOM for grid-connected systems</li>
          <li>Empanelled vendor for installation (MNRE approved)</li>
          <li>Net metering arrangement if planning grid-tied setup</li>
          <li>Inverter, battery (optional), structure, wiring, and maintenance plan</li>
        </ul>

        <h5>Steps to Install Solar:</h5>
        <ol>
          <li>Register on MNRE or DISCOM portal (e.g., <a href="https://pmsuryaghar.gov.in" target="_blank">PM Surya Ghar</a>)</li>
          <li>Choose MNRE-approved vendor</li>
          <li>Site survey and quotation</li>
          <li>Installation & inspection by DISCOM</li>
          <li>Subsidy claim and grid synchronization</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="mb-3">Solar Payback & Savings Calculator</h4>
        <form id="solarForm">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <label for="area" class="form-label">Available Rooftop Area (sq.ft)</label>
              <input type="number" class="form-control" id="area" required>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <label for="rate" class="form-label">Electricity Rate (â‚¹/unit)</label>
              <input type="number" step="0.1" class="form-control" id="rate" value="7" required>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <label for="cost" class="form-label">Installation Cost (â‚¹/kW)</label>
              <input type="number" class="form-control" id="cost" value="50000" required>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-3">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Calculate</button>
          </div>
        </form>
        <div id="results" class="result-box mt-4" style="display: none;">
          <h5>Estimates:</h5>
          <p><strong>System Size:</strong> <span id="kwSize"></span> kW</p>
          <p><strong>Energy Generated:</strong> <span id="energy"></span> kWh/month</p>
          <p><strong>Monthly Savings:</strong> â‚¹<span id="savings"></span></p>
          <p><strong>Total Cost:</strong> â‚¹<span id="totalCost"></span></p>
          <p><strong>Payback Period:</strong> <span id="payback"></span> years</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
   <div class="footer">
